bridge:
    play sound click
    if $data.crypto.metCrypto:
        choice:
            "A familiar figure appears to be lurking under The Old Iron Bridge..."
            "[Buy a bridge] <span class='prompt'>[[-1 ACTION]]</span>" if (>= $stats.actions.value 1):
                play sound spendAction
                set data.game_map.inMap false
                add_stat actions -1
                run transition_black bridge
                set data.global.cryptoBridgeDone true
                clear_dialog
            "<span class='prompt'>[[BACK]]</span>":
                jump game_map
    else:
        choice:
            "A peculiar guy appears to be lurking under The Old Iron Bridge..."
            "[Buy a bridge] <span class='prompt'>[[-1 ACTION]]</span>" if (>= $stats.actions.value 1):
                play sound spendAction
                set data.game_map.inMap false
                add_stat actions -1
                run transition_black bridge
                set data.global.cryptoBridgeDone true
                clear_dialog
            "<span class='prompt'>[[BACK]]</span>":
                jump game_map

    "The Test is calm. The source of the river is only a few miles away, in North Acres, but the lead mines nearby give the river little chance to flourish. The silver-grey industrial waste is occasionally polluted by some trout. "
    if (roll bridge_bridge_orb orb 40):
        talk orb talk "'The Old Iron Bridge' was originally forged out of cast iron in 1700 to celebrate both the turn of the century and Bluehills new (temporary) seat as the capital of the Imperial Province of Anglia."
        talk orb talk "It then collapsed a few weeks later, was rebuilt, proceeded to collapse again in 1735, and was rebuilt, blessed by several priests, and this time managed to stay standing."
        talk orb talk "For several decades. A bomb dropped by an Imperial Fokker hit it in 1923 and it collapsed. Anglia got her revenge. The Fokker was shot down by an Anglian Fucker Fighter Mk II a few days later."
        talk orb talk "It was rebuilt once more two years ago. I suggest not standing under it or on top of it for any longer than you have to."
        clear_dialog
    if $data.crypto.metCrypto:
        choice:
            "Lurking, like some kind of troll, under The Old Iron Bridge, is a familiar figure."
            "[Approach him]":
                talk orb talk "Not this guy again... Ghost, no making any rash financial decisions, okay?"
    else:
        choice:
            "Lurking, like some kind of troll, under The Old Iron Bridge, is a guy..."
            "[Approach him]":
                run skip
    clear_dialog
    "The Bridge Salesman appears to be scooping crabs out of the river and into a bucket. His hands are coated in a thick layer of mud and 'crab slime'."
    if (roll bridge_crabs_nasty nasty 20):
        set data.crypto.crabEat true
        talk nasty talk "Bridge crabs are good protein. Only way to get a balanced diet for us lactose intolerant bitches. The Thames is pretty much a five-star restaurant, innit?"
    else:
        wait 1000
    clear_dialog
    play music bigmoney
    run transition bridge_guy
    "The Bridge Salesman spots you, makes a face like you just caught him sniffing his sister's underwear, and leaps to his feet."
    clear_dialog
    talk bridge talk "Oh! Oh oh oh! Oh hello there, um... officer? Nothing untoward going on here! I'm just inspecting the mud, y'see!"
    clear_dialog
    "His eyes dart down to the bucket of crabs at his feet. One crab seems to be escaping, but another pinches it by the leg and drags it back inside so they can relitigate some discourse."
    clear_dialog
    talk bridge talk "The crabs? Pah! Wouldn't dream of eating their... their tender... succulent... protein rich flesh... oh y... yes... oh..."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "The Bridge Salesman licks his lips. His left eye twitches."
        "\\"Don't you remember me? I bought a Silly Sheep off of you the other day!\\"" if (has_item? sillySheep):
            "He squints at you for a moment, and then you see it, a sparkle of curiously '£' shaped recognition deep in his eye. He brushes off his suit, accidentaly streaking mud across it, and smiles."
            "His entire being changes. Jolts, as if he's been injected with cocaine."
            clear_dialog
            talk bridge talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! I remember you now, little lady! You're the proud owner of Silly Sheep #69! Congratulations! I hear the value of that little ditty is going sky high!"
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                "He motions towards the sky, his hand a little airplane. He makes a 'nyooom' noise."
                "\\"Am I a millionaire yet?\\"":
                    talk bridge talk "Materially? No. But *speculatively* you're a *billionaire*."
                    clear_dialog
                    "He smiles."
                    clear_dialog
                    choice:
                        talk bridge talk "I like that word, speculatively. Do you like that word?"
                        "\\"I love it! Awooooo!\\"":
                            talk bridge talk "That's right! Awoooo!"
        "\\"Didn't you try to sell me a drawing of a sheep the other day? I regret not buying it immensely and will do anything to buy it now.\\"" if (&& (!= (has_item? sillySheep) true) (== $data.crypto.metCrypto true)):
            talk bridge talk "Oh I'm sorry little lady! We're all out of Silly Sheep! A lot of new millionaires out there any day now!"
            talk bridge talk "Oceania will be quaking in its little boots when it sees Anglia hit the top of the stock market right when they thought it was in the bag! Oh yes oh yes oh yes!"
        "\\"Didn't you try to sell me a drawing of a sheep the other day? I didn't buy it, obviously. I'm no mark.\\" [Grab him by the collar and shake him about] \\"I'm no fucking mark!\\"" if (&& (!= (has_item? sillySheep) true) (== $data.crypto.metCrypto true)):
            talk bridge talk "Woah there little lady! There's no need for any roughhousing!"
            choice:
                talk bridge talk "I could tell you were no mark from miles away! You have such an air of intelligence! Yes mam, you'd have to be a mark *yourself* to try and swindle a savvy little lady like you!"
                "[Blush] \\"R-really? You think I'm smart? Do you think I'm cute too...\\" [Do this -> 👉👈]":
                    talk nasty talk "Oh fuck me. She's turning straight. I want out of here."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk bridge talk "Think? *Think!?* Little lady, I *know* you're smart! A real savvy girl! An investor! Like me!"
                "[Nod] \\"I smart.\\"":
                    talk bridge talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! A real savvy girl! An investor! Like me!"
            clear_dialog
            "He gestures to himself proudly."
        "[Point at the bucket of crabs] \\"That's a bucket of crabs.\\"":
            talk bridge talk "C- Crabs!? Oh!? Those little guys?"
            clear_dialog
            "He points at one of his buckets of mud and crabs."
            clear_dialog
            talk bridge talk "I- ignore them! T- they probably got in there by accident!"
            clear_dialog
            "He almost chokes on his own tongue and makes a sound like a frog getting pulled into a weir."
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                talk bridge talk "U- unless, uh... say, would giving you one to chew on make you stop asking about them?"
                "\\"I appreciate the offer, but I'm actually a lobster myself, so it would be too close to cannibalism for my tastes.\\" [Don't eat a bridge crab for personal reasons]" if $data.ghost.lobsterGirl:
                    talk bridge talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! Of course you are! I shouldn't have been so insensitive, I'm sorry little lobster!"
                "\\"Mmmm bridge crab in my tummy now please.\\" [Grab a bridge crab and stuff it into your mouth and start crunching on it while it pinches your tongue]":
                    play sound punch
                    run transition_pain
                    if (roll bridge_crab_orb orb 20):
                        talk orb talk "I hope for your sake the nutritional benefits of 'Bridge crabs' outweigh the permanent health effects of lead mine industrial waste."
                        clear_dialog
                    talk bridge talk "Oh my oh my oh my! You're one hungry little lady!"
                    talk bridge talk "Why if I had some of my genuine nutritional powder on me I'd give you a taste of that too! Always be on the lookout for new customers! A.B.B! Oh yes oh yes oh yes!"
                    clear_dialog
                    "He squints at you."
                    clear_dialog
                    choice:
                        talk bridge talk "Are you okay there miss? Your tongue seems to be bleeding."
                        "\\"It hurts a lot actually.\\"":
                            talk bridge talk "I'm sorry to hear that miss! You have to be careful with these here bridge crabs you know!"
                        "\\"It's fine.\\" [Lie]":
                            talk bridge talk "Wonderful! I'm glad for you miss!"
                "\\"No thank you, I'm homosexual. No bridge crabs for me.\\" [Don't eat a bridge crab on moral grounds]":
                    talk bridge talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! Of course you are! I shouldn't have been so insensitive, I'm sorry little lady!"
            clear_dialog
            "The Bridge Salesman thinks for a moment."
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                talk bridge talk "You know! I ought to invest in crabs some more! You can never invest in too many areas! It's called diversifying your portfolio, though I'm sure a stock savvy lady like yourself knows *all* about that!"
                "\\"Stocks.\\"":
                    talk lovely talk "You haven't the foggiest what you're on about do you, Ghost?"
                "\\"Stock market.\\"":
                    talk lovely talk "You haven't the foggiest what you're on about do you, Ghost?"
                "[Sneeze]":
                    set data.crypto.sneezed true
                    "You sneeze all over The Bridge Salesman. A bit of snot lands on his face, but he does not stop grinning."
                    "Without breaking eye contact he pulls out a small, slightly muddy handkerchief and cleans his face."
            clear_dialog
            if $data.crypto.metCrypto:
                "The Bridge Salesman seems to regain his usual pepped up charisma."
            else:
                "The Bridge Salesman seems to gain some kind of cocaine fuelled energy."
            if (roll bridge_sober_orb orb 20):
                talk orb talk "He's completely sober. This is just what he's like."
            else:
                wait 1000
    clear_dialog
    talk bridge talk "It's thanks to my own savvy investing that I own this beautiful beautiful boy."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "He pats the iron beam of the bridge."
        "\\"Holy crackers! You own this iron beam? That's bopper!\\"":
            talk bridge talk "Iron beam!? Oh no no my dear little lady!"
            clear_dialog
            "He sweeps his arms wide."
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                talk bridge talk "You're looking at the proud owner of this entire *bridge!*"
                "\\"Holy crackers!\\"":
                    talk bridge talk "Holy crackers is right, little lady! Though..."
                    clear_dialog
                    "He sidles up to you, puts a hand between his mouth and your ear, and whispers."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk bridge talk "...Between you and me, I'm thinking of selling it. Upsizing."
                    talk bridge talk "I'm eyeing up tower bridge, over in Lunden, you know? The bridge market is booming right now, and it's only going to go up, up, *up!*"
                    clear_dialog
                    "His points to the sky. Or the underside of a bridge, rather, since you're stood under a bridge."
    clear_dialog
    "The Bridge Salesman taps his foot and thinks."
    clear_dialog
    talk bridge talk "But if I don't need this bridge anymore it'll need a new owner..."
    clear_dialog
    play sound ding
    "He pulls a light bulb out of his pocket and somehow makes it turn on over his head. Ding!"
    clear_dialog
    talk bridge talk "Now here's an idea little lady! I could sell it to you!"
    clear_dialog
    talk lovely talk "How exciting! Our very own bridge!"
    if (roll bridge_mark_nasty nasty 20):
        talk nasty talk "Godammit Ghost don't buy a bridge you dumb whore."
    else:
        wait 1000
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk bridge talk "What do you think, little lady? Are you in the market for a bridge? Or do you just want to stay poor?"
        "\\"How much does this bridge cost?\\"":
            set data.bridge.priceText (numbverter $stats.money.value)
            choice:
                talk bridge talk "Let me answer that question with an unrelated question! How many good old patriotic Anglian pounds do you happen to have on your person right now?"
                "[Rifle through your pockets] Uhhhh... %{$data.bridge.priceText}?":
                    talk bridge talk "Well gee wilikers!"
                    clear_dialog
                    "The Bridge Salesmen puts on his best shocked face."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk bridge talk "That happens to be exactly how much this bridge costs! Fancy that!"
        "\\"I *have* been thinking I should buy a bridge lately. I'll take it.\\" [Hand over literally all your money]":
            unlock_achievement invest_bridge
            set_stat money 0
            play sound coins
            set data.crypto.hasBridge true
            set data.crypto.boughtBridge true
            set data.ghost.investor true
            if (quest_started? crypto):
                run skip
            else:
                start_quest crypto
            talk orb talk "..."
            clear_dialog
            talk lovely talk "Yip yip wheee! Now to become a landlady and rent it out to the city!"
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                talk bridge talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! An absolutely wonderful decision madam! You won't regret this! Not when bridge prices are rising up up up to the moon moon moon!"
                "\\"To the moon! Awooooo!\\"":
                    talk bridge talk "Yes! Awoooo! Haha!"
        "\\"Question. Could someone theoretically funge this bridge?\\"":
            choice:
                talk bridge talk "Oh no no no! No funging here, little lady! You think anyone else could build a bridge as sturdy as this one? Oh no no no!"
                "\\"I'm convinced. I'll take it.\\" [Hand over literally all of your money]":
                    unlock_achievement invest_bridge
                    set_stat money 0
                    play sound coins
                    set data.crypto.hasBridge true
                    set data.crypto.boughtBridge true
                    set data.ghost.investor true
                    if (quest_started? crypto):
                        run skip
                    else:
                        start_quest crypto
                    talk orb talk "..."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk lovely talk "Wheee! Now to become a landlady and rent it out to the city!"
                    clear_dialog
                    choice:
                        talk bridge talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! An absolutely wonderful decision little lady! You won't regret this! Not when bridge prices are rising up up up to the moon moon moon!"
                        "\\"To the moon! Awooooo!\\"":
                            talk bridge talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! Awoooo!"
                "\\"I'm still not completely convinced. Sorry.\\"":
                    talk bridge talk "That's your prerogative little lady! I'm not here to tell you how to use your money! I'm just here to give you advice to be ignored at your discretion!"
                    clear_dialog
                    "He shakes his head."
        "\\"I'm not sure I'm in the market for a bridge right now. That Silly Sheep you sold me is my one true soulmate. I'd die for it.\\" [Gasp] \\"Oh gods! It's not been funged, has it?\\" [Grab The Silly Sheep Salesman by the collar and shake him around while you start to cry] \\"Please tell me my Silly Sheep hasn't been funged!!!\\"" if (has_item? sillySheep):
            choice:
                talk bridge talk "O- oh no no no little lady! Your sheep is perfectly fine, and as unfunged as the day you bought it!"
                "\\"Oh thank the gods...\\" [Fall to your knees and sink into the mud] \\"I don't know what I'd do if Silly Sheep #69 got funged...\\"":
                    talk bridge talk "Well fortunately that can never ever happen, so there's no need to shed tears, oh yes oh yes oh yes! Here..."
                    clear_dialog
                    choice:
                        "He passes you a handkerchief. It's a little muddy."
                        "[Wipe your tears] \\"T- thank you...\\"":
                            talk bridge talk "No problem little lady! Us investors have to look out for one another, don't we!"
                            clear_dialog
                            "He pulls you back to your feet, and takes the handkerchief back with all the deftness of an expert pickpocket."
                            if (roll bridge_tissue_nasty nasty 40):
                                if $data.crypto.sneezed:
                                    talk nasty talk "He's going to wring your tears and snot out of the handkerchief and reuse it later. A.B.B."
                                else:
                                    talk nasty talk "He's going to wring your tears out of the handkerchief and reuse it later. A.B.B."
                            else:
                                wait 1000
        "\\"I'm just not in the market for a bridge right now, sorry sir.\\"":
            talk bridge talk "That's your prerogative little lady! I'm not here to tell you how to use your money! I'm just here to give you advice to be ignored at your discretion!"
            clear_dialog
            "He shakes his head."
    clear_dialog
    talk bridge talk "Anyhow, if that's all, please allow me to get on with my lunch, and you with your day."
    talk bridge talk "Though having had a chance to talk to you sadly means my day is only downhill from here!"
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "He winks at you. His smile sparkles."
        "[Blush] \\"Aww gee...\\"":
            talk nasty talk "I'm going to kill myself."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "The Bridge Salesman eyes one of the bridge crabs and licks his lips."
        "\\"Have fun eating crabs.\\" Bye bye. [Do a gay little wave and leave]" if $data.crypto.crabEat:
            talk bridge talk "Bye bye now! And remember! A.B.B!"
        "\\"Bye bye.\\" [Do a gay little wave and leave]":
            talk bridge talk "Bye bye now! And remember! A.B.B!"
    clear_dialog
    if $data.crypto.hasBridge:
        choice:
            talk orb talk "Please... please stop making bad financial decisions. Money is actually quite important, you know?"
            "If it was a bad financial decision I wouldn't have made it. <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
                play sound spendAction
                set data.crypto.metCrypto true
                jump goToGameMap
    else:
        choice:
            talk orb talk "Thank you, Ghost, for not making a terrible, terrible mistake."
            "There's still time. <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
                play sound spendAction
                set data.crypto.metCrypto true
                jump goToGameMap